The name refers to the large size and bright color of this species.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="33CB651CFFB6FFF65BE9F8FDE3D1F8AD" box="[240,1181,1859,1883]" pageId="23" pageNumber="22" type="distribution">
